OL,3,CAled Davies on the pressures of being
OL,4,Cone of Wales' best Paralympians
OL,6,FAled Davies is one of the most
OL,7,Fdecorated athletes Wales has ever
OL,8,Fproduced. He is also one of the most
OL,9,Frecognisable faces in the world of
OL,10,Fpara-athletics.
OL,12,FBorn with Hemimelia in his right leg,
OL,13,FDavies doesn't have a right foot,
OL,14,Ftibia or any ligaments in his knee.
OL,15,FNow at the age of 33, he has come to
OL,16,Fterms with the cards that life dealt
OL,17,Fhim.
OL,19,FBut his relationship with his
OL,20,Fdisability has not always been
OL,21,Fstraightforward.
