OL,3,CAled Davies on the pressures of being
OL,4,Cone of Wales' best Paralympians
OL,6,F"I grew up in an able-bodied world,"
OL,7,Fhe tells ITV Wales.
OL,9,F"I had no education of disability, no
OL,10,Fawareness of it. I didn't go to any
OL,11,Fdisability clubs, didn't have any
OL,12,Ffriends with a disability. I knew my
OL,13,Fleg was different, you know, I knew I
OL,14,Fwas born different and I always tried
OL,15,Fto hide it.
OL,17,F"I had a lot of stick growing up, like
OL,18,Fmost people who are different, but it
OL,19,Fmade me who I am. It sounds really sad
OL,20,Fwhen I talk about it now because I
OL,21,Ffeel like - why was I ashamed?
