OL,3,CAled Davies on the pressures of being
OL,4,Cone of Wales' best Paralympians
OL,6,FDavies has become the best in the
OL,7,Fworld in both the shot-put and discus.
OL,8,FHe hasn't lost an event that he's
OL,9,Fentered for a decade.
OL,11,FIt's a level of dominance that is
OL,12,Falmost unparalleled, and yet there is
OL,13,Fa harsh reality to life as a para-
OL,14,Fathlete.
OL,16,FDespite sitting on top of the world,
OL,17,FDavies has no private sponsors and
OL,18,Frelies on funding from UK Sport.
