OL,3,CAled Davies on the pressures of being
OL,4,Cone of Wales' best Paralympians
OL,6,F"It's a tough one because I'm in a
OL,7,Fposition where I'm so grateful for
OL,8,Feverything I've had. When I was a
OL,9,Fchild, looking at being a professional
OL,10,Fathlete, that wasn't an option. That
OL,11,Favenue didn't exist for anyone with a
OL,12,Fdisability.
OL,14,F"But it's hard. We're one of the only
OL,15,Fcountries that doesn't give athletes a
OL,16,Fcash prize for medals at the Games.
