OL,3,CAled Davies on the pressures of being
OL,4,Cone of Wales' best Paralympians
OL,6,F"A lot of us can't buy a house because
OL,7,Fwe haven't got that cushion to build
OL,8,Fdeposits. I could probably count on
OL,9,Fone hand the number of athletes who
OL,10,Fare able to get mortgages."
OL,12,FDespite the challenges, the Welshman's
OL,13,Fmedal record is nothing short of
OL,14,Fremarkable.
