OL,3,CAled Davies on the pressures of being
OL,4,Cone of Wales' best Paralympians
OL,6,FIn total, he has won 12 gold medals at
OL,7,Fthe European Championships, nine golds
OL,8,Fand one silver at the World
OL,9,FChampionships, one gold and one silver
OL,10,Fat the Commonwealth Games, and three
OL,11,Fgolds and one bronze at the
OL,12,FParalympics.
OL,14,FHe also happens to be the current
OL,15,Fworld record holder in both the shot
OL,16,Fput and the discus.
