OL,3,CAled Davies on the pressures of being
OL,4,Cone of Wales' best Paralympians
OL,6,F"It's surreal," he says with a
OL,7,Fchuckle. "I mean, I still feel like
OL,8,Fthe kid that had aspirations to make a
OL,9,FParalympic Games and bring home a gold
OL,10,Fmedal and to think that I'm going into
OL,11,Fmy fourth games now with still the
OL,12,Fsame fire in my belly and still the
OL,13,Fsame hunger for the same colour - I
OL,14,Ffeel very privileged and lucky to have
OL,15,Fa dream job."
OL,17,FBut all that success brings a pressure
OL,18,Fto deliver every time he steps into
OL,19,Fthe arena.
