OL,3,CAled Davies on the pressures of being
OL,4,Cone of Wales' best Paralympians
OL,6,FAnd it also means that he has a giant
OL,7,Ftarget on his back with rivals
OL,8,Fqueueing up to knock him off the top
OL,9,Fspot.
OL,11,F"It's the hardest challenge," he says.
OL,12,F"Every major champs I go into, there's
OL,13,Fa target on my back. Everyone wants to
OL,14,Fbeat me and unfortunately everyone
OL,15,Fwants me to lose.
