OL,3,CAled Davies on the pressures of being
OL,4,Cone of Wales' best Paralympians
OL,6,F"It does get boring seeing the same
OL,7,Fguy being so dominant. I get that.
OL,8,FBut, at the same time, I'm the one at
OL,9,Fthe forefront pushing and making sure
OL,10,Fthat I am better than everyone else
OL,11,Fand that even on a bad day, my throws
OL,12,Fare still further than everyone else.
OL,14,F"I've learned over the years with my
OL,15,Fexperience, if you stop thinking about
OL,16,Fthe medals and just think about the
OL,17,Fperformance and execute that
OL,18,Fperformance, you will go home with the
OL,19,Fcolour that you came for."
