OL,3,CAled Davies on the pressures of being
OL,4,Cone of Wales' best Paralympians
OL,6,FIf he's to notch up another medal in
OL,7,FParis this weekend, Davies will also
OL,8,Fhave to overcome considerable injury
OL,9,Fproblems.
OL,11,FFor two years, he's been battling
OL,12,Fosteitis pubis, which causes
OL,13,Fconsiderable pain and swelling in the
OL,14,Fgroin.
OL,16,FThere is a danger that disaster could
OL,17,Fstrike when Davies puts everything
OL,18,Finto his throws at the Stade de France.
OL,20,FBut that risk is something he has long
OL,21,Fsince made peace with.
