OL,3,CAled Davies on the pressures of being
OL,4,Cone of Wales' best Paralympians
OL,6,F"It is very, very annoying," he
OL,7,Fexplains. "With my adductor being so
OL,8,Ftight and pulling on the hip, there is
OL,9,Fobviously that risk that I could come
OL,10,Fround and crank my right leg and
OL,11,Fpotentially pull my adductor off the
OL,12,Fbone.
OL,14,F"But my opinion at this point is,
OL,15,Flook, you get me to the start line and
OL,16,Fif I'm going to break or I'm going to
OL,17,Fget injured, it's going to be out
OL,18,Fthere doing everything I can to defend
OL,19,Fthat gold medal and representing my
OL,20,Fcountry."
