OL,3,CAled Davies on the pressures of being
OL,4,Cone of Wales' best Paralympians
OL,6,FOn the Paris Games, he concludes:
OL,7,F"This is going to be the hardest one
OL,8,Fof my career. It's going to be a
OL,9,Fdogfight. Everyone is geared up and I
OL,10,Fthink they can see that I am on the
OL,11,Fropes a bit.
OL,13,F"I think they underestimate what I'm
OL,14,Fgoing to bring to the table this
OL,15,Fsummer. But for me, this is
OL,16,Feverything."
